node.text: Totally caught off guard!!! Wow!! What a beautiful surprise to kick off Valentine’s Day weekend!! My baby @roccstarmusic you did that! Off to Aspen!

node.text: Fashion isn’t the only thing I’m into. Having multiple businesses & incomes is what I’m on! @roccstarmusic and I started a trucking company awhile back and have since then, added more trucks to our fleet! Transportation is highly important, getting goods to and from businesses to another to keep the demands of supply to families keeps the economy moving.

node.text: My beautiful, smart, witty, sweet, helpful, loving, loyal, Leo, Amani. Happy birthday!!!! May God continue to bless you, and light the way! You leave so many imprints on other’s hearts. Such a humanitarian, animal lover, and overall good soul. Amani is the type that will stop and give her food to people without housing, and has no malice in her heart. You go with me everywhere and have become my best friend. Never even had terrible 2’s, and have been such a behaved child since day one. Having you has been one of my most happiest moments in life. May you get everything you want out of life, and I will be the power house behind it!! @amanievans
